# Branding and Styling Guidelines

## MeteoScientific Brand Colors
Define these CSS custom properties in [src/css/custom.css](mdc:src/css/custom.css):

```css
--metsci-primary: #D94A18;   /* Troposphere Red - Primary */
--metsci-red: #FA7F2A;       /* Solar Haze */
--metsci-blue: #18A7D9;      /* Jet Stream Blue */
--metsci-white: #FCF5F0;     /* Cirrus White */
--metsci-black: #000000;     /* Stratosphere Black */
```

## Brand Assets
- **Logo Files**: [static/img/metsci_pro_media/](mdc:static/img/metsci_pro_media)
