## Typography and Layout
- Use Docusaurus default typography with MetSci color overrides
- Maintain consistent spacing and hierarchy
- Ensure accessibility standards are met
- Test on both light and dark themes

## Component Styling
- Keep styles modular using CSS modules (.module.css files)
- Use CSS custom properties for consistent theming
- Follow Docusaurus styling conventions
- Reference examples in [src/components/](mdc:src/components) subdirectories
